Real Soon Now for the last couple of years, I gather due to
Stupid Publisher Tricks.  It'd be nice if it finally happens.

Meanwhile, A Local Cypherpunk has my copy (relatively large print
paperback, found for about $4 in a used book store);
there was at some point a plot to scan and OCR the thing,
though I'm not sure that ever materialized.

>>       Used book stores -- sigh! Sure wish I could afford to quit the 
